Class AttributeValueFuser<ValueType,RecordType extends Matchable & Fusible<SchemaElementType>,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>

  • Type Parameters:
    ValueType - the type of the values that are fused
    RecordType - the type that represents a record

    public abstract class AttributeValueFuser<ValueType,RecordType extends Matchable & Fusible<SchemaElementType>,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
extends AttributeFuser<RecordType,SchemaElementType>
    Abstract super class for all Fusers tailored to specific attributes (hence the ValueType). Ignores schema correspondences.
    Author:
    Oliver Lehmberg (oli@dwslab.de)
